(3, 'What our guests say?', 'what-our-guests-say', '<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div><img src="http://demo.peacenepal.com/ibook/public/uploads/testimonials/testimonial_1469621705.jpg" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div><strong>Lee Li Er (Singapore)</strong><br />\r\n&quot; Our 1st trekking trip to Nepal was a great success!! Thank you so much! Big thanks to the fantastic guides and amazing porters in Divine Nepal. Throughout the trek the guides especially Pemba were very attentive, always enquiring if we slept well. Thank you for a truly unforgettable experience &quot;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n', NULL, 'What our guests say?', 'What our guests say?', 'What our guests say?', NULL, 1, 1, '1', '0', '1', '2016-07-28 08:56:20', '2016-07-28 09:27:07', '2016-07-28 09:27:07'),
(4, 'About Us', 'about-us', '<p>In 2015, we established Nepal Easy Tours &amp; Travel in Nepal as one of the strong Outbound and inbound agent with a passion to provide a highly personalised service organizing treks and tours for avid travelers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Nepal Easy Tours &amp; Travel managed by a highly qualified team who has among them more than 25 years of working experience in the tourism industry. As travel professionals and outdoor enthusiasts, the team has managed numerous climbs, expeditions and adventurous activities. We have spread our wings to specialise adventure and leisure travel outside Nepal like Sikkim, Tibet and Bhutan. Company also running one of the strong Outbound tour agent and operate regular tour to Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand, Indonesia, Sri&nbsp; Lanka and Cambodia. .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In the recent years, we have received numerous requests from many of you who have traveled with us to expand our palette of travel itineraries. We are doing so and will continue to advocate an all-rounder experience with a fine balance among culture, history and adventure in our itineraries. And of course, exotic locations with lots of varied adventures!</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We want to offer each of you who travel with us an enriching experience that lasts beyond each trip. In these uncertain days it is all the more important that we get out and explore our wonderful world. It is through travel we breakdown prejudice, build understanding and create a better and more caring world.</p>\r\n', NULL, 'About Us', 'About Us', 'About Us', NULL, 1, 1, '1', '0', '1', '2016-08-07 12:13:20', '2016-08-07 17:26:53', NULL);

