(41, 13, 6, '7 Days Nepal Escape Tour', '7-days-nepal-escape-tour', '7 Days Nepal Escape Tour', '7 Days Nepal Escape Tour', '7 Days Nepal Escape Tour', '<p>Landlocked between the soaring snow-capped peaks of the Himalayas and the marshy grasslands along the border with India, Nepal is a country of immense natural beauty and a bounty of outdoor pleasures. Home to the majestic Himalayas, Nepal offers travellers unrivalled mountain trekking coupled with breathtaking scenery, ancient Buddhist temples and monasteries, plus centuries of sacred history. Take in the rich 2000-year history of Nepal&rsquo;s capital, Kathmandu, explore the ancient trading town of Bhaktapur, visit the birthplace of Buddha in Lumbini or track exotic local wildlife in Chitwan National Park.</p>\r\n', '<p>Day 01: KATHMANDU (D)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDay 02: KATHMANDU &ndash; CHITWAN NATIONAL PARK (B,L,D)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDay 03: CHITWAN NATIONAL PARK (B,L,D)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDay 04: CHITWAN NATIONAL PARK- POKHARA (B,L,D)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDay 05: POKHARA-SARANGKOT-POKHARA (B,L,D)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDay 06: POKHARA &ndash; KATHMANDU (B,L,D)<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDay 07: KATHMANDU (B)<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Private A/C transportation including airport transfer</li>\r\n	<li>1 way Pokhara &ndash; Kathmandu domestic flight</li>\r\n	<li>Personal English speaking tour guide</li>\r\n	<li>Accommodation</li>\r\n	<li>Meals as per itinerary</li>\r\n	<li>Entrance and activity fees</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '<ul>\r\n	<li>Nepal visa (apply upon arrival)</li>\r\n	<li>Travel insurance</li>\r\n	<li>All alcoholic and other beverages</li>\r\n	<li>All personal expenses</li>\r\n	<li>Liabilities of loss, theft and damages</li>\r\n	<li>Tips</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', '8', '', NULL, '', NULL, 0, 0, NULL, '', NULL, 700.00, 640.00, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 9, 1, 1, '1', '1', '1', '2016-07-04 13:48:55', '2016-07-27 11:59:52', '2016-07-27 11:59:52');
